• Get involved

Bitesize culture from Brum's tech scene

It’s well known that people in the City of 1000 Trades rarely promote themselves. So, we thought: why not use our experience in Tech Events to showcase the region's amazing people beyond the industry we know? This is BrumTechTapas, and we love people making a difference, whatever they do.

Photo by Raphael Lionel Photography

Upcoming event

October 2020

24th March 2021, 7:00pm

Due to COVID, we’re launching online for now. In the future our events will be hosted at Iron House Gallery in the Jewellery Quarter.
